# React Post Polling App

This is a simple React application that periodically polls an API to fetch new posts and displays them in a table. The application fetches new posts every 10 seconds and adds them to the existing list of posts.

## Features

- Periodically fetches new posts from the Hacker News API.
- Displays the title, URL, created_at, and author of each post in a table.
- Automatically adds new posts to the existing list without refreshing the page.
- Increases the page count in each subsequent GET request to fetch new posts.


